40|$|We {{investigate}} {{a connection between}} generalized Fibonacci numbers and renewal theory for stochastic processes. Using Blackwell's <b>renewal</b> <b>theorem</b> we find an approximation to the generalized Fibonacci numbers. With the help of error estimates in the <b>renewal</b> <b>theorem</b> we figure out an explicit representation. © 2012 Elsevier B. V...|$|E
